{"timestamp":" 302.200557562s","level":"DEBUG","fields":{"message":"Adding tool results to context","results":"[ToolResult { name: ToolName(\"shell\"), call_id: Some(ToolCallId(\"call_00_JTVyX0ElvrCGWBrPQCk3tyU2\")), output: ToolOutput { is_error: false, values: [Text(\"<shell_output\\n  command=\\\"bd show bmx-c7z 2>&1\\\"\\n  shell=\\\"/usr/bin/zsh\\\"\\n  description=\\\"Show bmx-c7z bead\\\"\\n  exit_code=\\\"0\\\"\\n>\\n<stdout\\n  total_lines=\\\"26\\\"\\n><![CDATA[✓ bmx-c7z [EPIC] · Enforce Strict TEA State Flow   [● P2 · CLOSED]\\nOwner: Megatherium · Assignee: badmux/polecats/rust · Type: epic\\nCreated: 2026-04-24 · Updated: 2026-04-30\\nClose reason: no-changes: all child beads (bmx-c7z.1, bmx-c7z.2) already completed and closed. MR bmx-wisp-owj already submitted.\\n\\nDESCRIPTION\\nattached_molecule: bmx-wisp-6vde attached_formula: mol-polecat-work attached_at:\\n2026-04-30T12:34:50Z dispatched_by: mayor                                       \\n                                                                                \\nThe codebase suffers from leakage of concurrency primitives (atomics, mutexes)  \\ninto UI models (like internal/ui/center/Model). These must be replaced with     \\nstrict Bubbletea message passing to prevent ghost states.                       \\n\\n\\nDEPENDS ON\\n  → ○ bmx-wisp-6vde: (EPIC) mol-polecat-work ● P2\\n\\nCHILDREN\\n  ↳ ✓ bmx-c7z.1: Refactor center.Model to eliminate atomic state ● P2\\n  ↳ ✓ bmx-c7z.2: Refactor AgentManager to emit TEA messages ● P2\\n  ✓ 2/2 complete (100%) — eligible for close\\n\\nCOMMENTS\\n  2026-04-30 11:36 badmux/polecats/rust\\n    MR created: bmx-wisp-owj                                                        \\n]]>\\n</stdout>\\n</shell_output>\")] } }, ToolResult { name: ToolName(\"shell\"), call_id: Some(ToolCallId(\"call_01_qikDk0wqogxn47PIz5X1SNyJ\")), output: ToolOutput { is_error: false, values: [Text(\"<shell_output\\n  command=\\\"bd show bmx-zlc.1 2>&1\\\"\\n  shell=\\\"/usr/bin/zsh\\\"\\n  description=\\\"Show bmx-zlc.1 bead\\\"\\n  exit_code=\\\"0\\\"\\n>\\n<stdout\\n  total_lines=\\\"18\\\"\\n><![CDATA[◇ bmx-zlc.1 · Add gocyclo and funlen linters   [● P2 · HOOKED]\\nOwner: Megatherium · Assignee: badmux/polecats/rust · Type: task\\nCreated: 2026-04-24 · Updated: 2026-04-30\\n\\nDESCRIPTION\\nattached_molecule: bmx-wisp-8oe1 attached_formula: mol-polecat-work attached_at:\\n2026-04-30T13:05:09Z dispatched_by: mayor                                       \\n                                                                                \\nUpdate .golangci.yml and .golangci.strict.yml to include gocyclo/cyclop (e.g.   \\nmax 15) and funlen. Fix or skip existing violations.                            \\n\\n\\nPARENT\\n  ↑ ○ bmx-zlc: (EPIC) Implement Architectural Linting ● P2\\n\\nDEPENDS ON\\n  → ○ bmx-wisp-8oe1: (EPIC) mol-polecat-work ● P2\\n]]>\\n</stdout>\\n</shell_output>\")] } }, ToolResult { name: ToolName(\"shell\"), call_id: Some(ToolCallId(\"call_02_P0Bq6vbnmHu8PLmX3zbzdFqL\")), output: ToolOutput { is_error: false, values: [Text(\"<shell_output\\n  command=\\\"ps aux | grep -i \\\"[c]laude\\\\|[f]orge\\\" 2>&1 | head -20\\\"\\n  shell=\\\"/usr/bin/zsh\\\"\\n  description=\\\"Check running agent processes\\\"\\n  exit_code=\\\"0\\\"\\n>\\n<stdout\\n  total_lines=\\\"9\\\"\\n><![CDATA[sloth     871935  0.0  0.2 4461112 74252 pts/10  Ssl+ 14:55   0:12 forge -i -p [GAS TOWN] mayor <- human • 2026-04-30T14:55 • cold-start  Check your hook and mail, then act on the hook if present: 1. `gt hook` - shows hooked work (if any) 2. `gt mail inbox` - check for messages 3. If work is hooked → execute it immediately 4. If nothing hooked → wait for instructions\\nsloth    1199307  0.0  0.1 3477620 43796 pts/27  Ssl+ 19:45   0:00 forge -i -p [GAS TOWN] deacon <- daemon • 2026-04-30T19:45 • patrol  I am Deacon. Start patrol: run gt deacon heartbeat, then check gt hook. If no hook, run gt sling mol-deacon-patrol deacon, then execute the hook it creat